          <l n="17"><milestone unit="para"/>Hanc cum caminis igne crepantibus  </l>
            <l n="18">Iussisse fertur praecipitem dari  </l>
            <l n="19">Priscus, ueneni fonte nocentior,  </l>
             <l n="20">(Nam sic feralem tempore sordido   </l>
            <l n="21">Dixere sanctae uirginis arbitrum),  </l>
            <l n="22">Huius ministri dum <choice n="0.92"><sic n="39">cuperent</sic><corr n="3">eriperent</corr></choice> nimis  </l>
            <l n="23"><sic>Fomacis</sic> escae tradere martyram,  </l>
            <l n="24">Lux tunc Olympi luce serenior  </l>
             <l n="25">Opus remouit saeua <choice n="0.5"><sic n="4">uolentium</sic><corr n="4">nolentium</corr></choice>,   </l>
            <l n="26">Cum uoce monstrant qui gladium simul:  </l>
            <l n="27">"Nos hinc precamur dirige tartaro,  </l>
            <l n="28">Nam nostra sanctam non uiolat manus".  </l> 

          <l n="29"><milestone unit="para"/>Turgescit illi felle iecur calens:  </l>
             <l n="30">Mox saxa fossas <choice><sic>nerbera</sic><corr>uerbera</corr></choice> bestias,   </l>
            <l n="31">Maius uenenum blanditias parat,  </l>
            <l n="32">Quibus uirago fortiter obstitit.  </l> 

          

